OL,4,G1805FGormiti: The New Era
OL,5,     GThe Showdown. The Scions must
OL,6,     Gdraw on all their training to
OL,7,     Grise above overwhelming odds.
OL,8,     GHowever, when even Fusion is not
OL,9,     Genough, the team is forced to
OL,10,     Gfind new reserves of faith and
OL,11,     Gwill.
OL,12,G1835FTotal Drama Island: Reboot
OL,13,     GHaulin' n' Ballin'. The fate of
